" Unmap Surround plugin's "ds" mapping during BufExplorer operation.
augroup local_bufExplorer
    autocmd!
    autocmd BufEnter \[BufExplorer\] unmap ds
    autocmd BufLeave \[BufExplorer\] nmap ds <Plug>Dsurround
